Considered the "Holy Grail" in skincare, Vitamin C in its purest form has many beneficial effects on our skin. Vitamin C can reduce the look of fine lines and wrinkles, shrinks large pores, fade dark spots brighten complexion, protect your skin from free radical damage and more.

settings.heading: What is stable and pure
settings.description: Stable and pure means our serum uses Vitamin C in its purest form (A powder!) and will not oxidize - meaning you always get the best results day and night.

settings.heading: Is this safe for sensitive skin?
settings.description: Our Serum is safe for all skintypes! If you find any irritation, use every other night until your skin adjusts.

settings.heading: how often should I apply?
settings.description: For best results, use our Vitamin C Serum everyday (day and night).

settings.heading: Do I need To Avoid The Sun When Using?
settings.description: Universal C Refiner Vitamin C Brightening Serum is a powerful and effective way to protect your skin from sun damage, but it doesn't replace the need for SPF. We have the C Refiner Vitamin C Serum with SPF 50 Mineral Sunscreen that is the perfect 2 in 1 step to correct and protect your skin from UVA/B damage.

settings.heading: Great Skin Starts with the Right Chemistry.

settings.text: Cutting through the clutter with chemist-founded, clinically proven formulas.

settings.title: 20% Pure & Stable
settings.text: No beauty brand had yet to formulate this notoriously unstable ingredient in its purest form (L-ascorbic acid) at 20%, its optimal strength.

settings.title: No oxidation
settings.text: Our delivery system is impervious to oxidation, giving you optimal results every time.

settings.title: Triple patented
settings.text: Our proprietary elastomer gels not only stabilize pure L-ascorbic acid, but also provide an elegant texture and undeniably velvety matte finish to the skin.
